data.description: This 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms No HOA home has a split floor concept giving you the privacy you have been looking for in a home. It's perfectly located on a dead end street with no Thru Traffic, making it a quiet location and a great place to live at. You can find this home's laundry in the garage (washer and dryer not included) for your convenience and comfort. This home features a new metal roof (2021), and ceramic tile throughout the house. Its spacious fenced lot and screened back porch, offers you and your guest the perfect spot for a "Sunday's BBQ". A MUST SEE home!!!
